@startuml
title EventQueue Producer-Consumer Flow
skinparam shadowing false

participant "Producer (callback/thread)" as Producer
participant EventQueue
participant Application
participant "Dispatch Path" as Dispatch

Producer -> EventQueue : Add(EventVariant)
Application -> EventQueue : Drain()
EventQueue --> Application : vector<EventVariant>
Application -> Dispatch : process batch

note right of EventQueue
Queue is synchronized and
stores platform events only.
end note

@enduml
